Radha!
- Kamu keras kepala, kan?

00:19:03.280 --> 00:19:04.960
Aku akan mendobrak pintunya.

00:19:21.640 --> 00:19:23.080
Kemana kamu pergi, Mohan?

00:19:23.960 --> 00:19:25.640
Apa maksudmu?  Apakah kamu gila?

00:19:25.720 --> 00:19:27.400
Maksudku, kembalikan pakaianku padaku.

00:19:28.720 --> 00:19:30.400
Oh!  Maaf.

00:19:34.880 --> 00:19:35.960
Di Sini.

00:19:40.960 --> 00:19:42.880
Mohan, tutup pintunya.

